 BARELY 24 hours after 17 persons were killed at Gonan-Rogo village, another eight persons have been reported killed in a fresh attack on three communities in Kajuru Local Government Area of Kaduna State. The Nation gathered that the attack took place between Tuesday evening and yesterday morning. President of the Adara Development Association (ADA), Awema Maisamari, told newsmen that the latest attack took place in Bakin-Kogi, Idanu and Makyali communities. Police spokesman Mohammed Jalige did not respond to calls for confirmation of the incident   